name: Agate & Garnet Necklace
description: An earthy "crazy lace" agate stone is accompanied by a glittering faceted garnet. They are both tucked into a sterling silver bezel setting measuring 1" x 1.25". The silver has been given a soft patina, which complements the natural tones of the agate, and contrasts beautifully with the sparkle of the garnet. The pendant is suspended on a 19" sterling silver chain.

name: Dendritic Opal Necklace
description: A stunning dendritic opal rests within a gorgeous scalloped bezel setting. The bold gemstone is a soft lavender-gray hue with unique black and white inclusions. The silver pendant is generous in size at 1.5"x2" and glides along its sterling chain on a hidden tube bail. This one-of-a-kind necklace is 19" in length and is finished with a sterling silver toggle clasp.

name: Seedpod Earrings
description: Dotted discs of sterling silver swing boldly from elegant handformed earwires. The gently curved discs have been oxidized and polished by hand to accentuate the raised texture and to give these earrings a well-worn quality. The discs measure just over 1" in diameter, and these earrings are approximately 1.75" in total length.

name: Eventide Earrings
description: Gentle curves and subtle details make these earrings easy to wear every day. The sterling silver drops measure 1.25" long and .5" wide. They swing from elongated sterling earwires, making these earrings 2" in total length.

name: Labradorite and Leather Necklace
description: A captivating labradorite stone pairs beautifully with rustic leather cord to create a necklace that is bold and unique, but entirely wearable. The faceted stone is primarily gray in color, but flashes blue, green, and gold when it catches the light. The sterling bezel setting has been given a soft patina to give the necklace an aged, organic quality. The labradorite pendant is accompanied by sterling silver beads which slide along the 19" genuine leather cord. The necklace is finished with a silver hook and eye clasp.

name: Polka Dot Earrings
description: These sterling silver earrings have a modern shape, an elegant curve, and a whimsical polka dot pattern. The textured plates measure just over .5"at their widest point and swing from elongated handformed earwires. The earrings are 2.25" in total length.

name: Ruby Drop Earrings
description: Rustic, deep red rubies rest at the ends of elongated sterling silver teardrops. The silver has been hammered and oxidized to give these elegant earrings a weathered quality. The teardrops are each 1.75" long, and the earrings are 2" in total length. Only one pair available.

name: Plume Agate Necklace
description: A beautiful plume agate stone glows in hues of lavender and crimson. This unique stone is surrounded by a scalloped sterling silver bezel setting measuring nearly 1.5" wide. The bold silver setting has been oxidized to give it a more casual feel. This pendant glides along a 19" silver chain and is finished with a sterling lobster clasp.

name: Enclosure Earrings
description: These sterling silver earrings are generous in size, but light enough for everyday wear. Modern silver circles have been formed by hand to maintain a beautiful organic quality in the shape. The circles have been hammered at the top and bottom to add interest and dimension, and the entire earring has been given a gentle curve, making these earrings interesting from any angle. The earrings measure nearly 1.5" across and approximately 1.75" from the top of the earwire to the bottom of the silver circle.

name: Lemon Quartz Earrings
description: Faceted lemon quartz stones dangle from elongated sterling earwires. The silver had been oxidized to contrast with the sparkle of the faceted stones. These earrings measure just under 2" in total length.

name: Aquamarine Oval Necklace
description: A lovely pale blue aquamarine cabochon is surrounded in sterling silver and suspended on a genuine brown leather cord. The necklace is 19" in total length and is finished with a sterling hook and eye clasp. The aquamarine pendant is .75" wide.

name: Labradorite Stud Earrings
description: These simple post earrings contain a pair of lovely labradorite cabochons, measuring 8mm in diameter. These captivating gemstones are primarily dark gray in color, but flash hues of blue, green, and purple when they catch the light. The sterling silver bezel settings have been softly oxidized to bring a weathered, more organic feel to these earrings. These earrings come with clear rubber backs.

name: Weathered Disc Earrings
description: These simple silver earrings make it easy to wear handmade every day. The 3/8" weathered discs swing from handformed sterling earwires. The earrings are 1" in total length and go with just about everything!

name: Scalloped Cuff Bracelet
description: This simple cuff bracelet is solid sterling silver, accented with a feminine scalloped motif. The pattern has been darkly oxidized, while the rest of the bracelet has a bright satin finish.  This bracelet is 3/8" wide and 2mm thick, giving it a nice weight and making it a casual, yet special piece that you'll wear for years to come. This cuff is well-suited for a 6-7" wrist.

name: Triangle Rectangle Earrings
description: These modern, understated post earrings are 5/8" in length just 1/4" wide. The post is positioned at the top of the earring, so that the hand stamped triangle hangs just below the earlobe. All metal is .925 sterling silver. These post earrings come with clear plastic backs.

name: Petal Pattern Cuff
description: Modern design and feminine pattern come together to make this classic cuff a piece you'll wear for years to come. The petal pattern scattered across the surface has been oxidized and polished to give this bracelet a weathered appearance. Made from 1" wide solid sterling silver, this cuff has a nice weight and is well suited for a 6-7" wrist.

name: Apatite Ring
description:
This bold, organic ring features a beautiful deep teal blue apatite gemstone surrounded in sterling silver. The apatite cabochon is set in an asymmetrical scalloped bezel setting, and rests atop a wide hammered band. The bezel plate is nearly 1" wide and the hammered band is approximately 3/8" wide, making this chunky ring easy to wear. 

Only one more available!

name: Little Lace Necklace
description: Reminiscent of vintage lace, yet modern in design, this necklace is simple and feminine and perfect for everyday wear. The hand-cut scalloped silver pendant is 1.75" long and is suspended on sterling silver chain. The pendant has been oxidized and polished to a satin finish to bring out the small stamped details. The necklace measures approximately 18" in total length and is finished with a sterling lobster clasp.

name: Little Star Studs
description: These lovely little post earrings are weathered and casual and perfect for everyday wear. A pair of sterling silver domes have been stamped with tiny little stars. The domes are bezel set in sterling silver and the earrings have been oxidized and polished to give them an aged appearance. The earrings measure just 6mm in diameter.

name: Scalloped Ring
description:
This bold but simple ring is a solid sterling silver band, accented with a feminine scalloped motif along one edge. The delicate pattern has been oxidized to help it stand out and to give it a bit of vintage appeal. The ring measures just over .5" wide and is slightly fluted at each end for a more comfortable fit. Due to the width of the band, the fit will feel smaller than normal. You may want to order a whole size larger than your usual finger size.

Each ring is made to order. Please select the size you'd like (taking into consideration the width of the band) and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping. If you have shorter fingers and need a slightly narrower band, please contact me immediately after ordering.

name: Fickle Earrings
description: These unique, modern earrings are balanced, but asymmetrical. Slim rectangles of sterling silver are marked with a group of three oxidized lines near the top of one earring, and just a pair of lines on the other. The rectangles are each 1.75" long and have a brushed satin finish. The handformed sterling earwires add a bit of length, making these earrings a total of 2.5" from top to bottom.

name: Turquoise Gathering Bracelet
description: A lovely little collection of turquoise stones creates a delicate, organic focal point for this casual bracelet. The genuine turquoise nuggets are interspersed with several Thai silver beads, and they rest at the end of a beautifully distressed leather cord. The bracelet measures 8” in total length and is finished with a sterling hook and eye clasp. This bracelet matches the Turquoise Gathering Necklace.

name: Turquoise Gathering Necklace
description: A lovely little collection of turquoise stones creates a delicate, organic focal point for this casual necklace. The genuine turquoise nuggets are interspersed with several Tibetan silver beads, creating an elongated pendant that is suspended between lengths of beautifully distressed leather cord. The necklace measures approximately 20” in total length and is finished with a sterling hook and eye clasp. This necklace matches the Turquoise Gathering Bracelet.

name: Secret Garden Cuff
description: Made of solid sterling silver, this cuff is simple in design, but contains some lovely hidden details. While the top of the bracelet appears smooth and round, the underside had been widened and stamped with a delicate flower motif...adding just a hint of femininity to this otherwise understated piece.  This cuff is well-suited for a 6-7" wrist, and is a great way to wear handmade every day.

name: Faceted Prehnite Earrings
description: These perfectly simple earrings feature a pair of beautiful faceted prehnite gemstones. The rectangular stones are a cloudy sea-green color, and swing from delicate sterling earwires. The prehnite gemstones are approximately .5" tall, and the earrings measure just over 1" in total length.

name: Simple Silver Tube Bracelet
description: This understated bracelet features a smooth sterling silver tube, which slides freely along a dark brown genuine leather cord. The tube measures 1.5" long and the bracelet is 8" in total length. The bracelet is finished by a sterling silver hook and eye clasp. This piece looks great worn with other bracelets!

name: Teardrop Earrings
description: These modern earrings are large enough to make a statement, but light enough for everyday wear. The elegant sterling silver drops have been hammered along the bottom edge, and measure over 1" at their widest point. The teardrops swing from sterling handformed earwires, and the earrings are approximately 2.25" in total length.

name: Seedling Earrings
description: Dotted drops of sterling silver dangle gently from elegant elongated earwires. The silver petals have been oxidized and polished by hand to accentuate the raised texture and to give these earrings a well-worn quality. The drops measure .5" at their widest point, and these earrings are approximately 1.75" in total length.

name: Organic Circle Earrings
description: Two irregular, organic sterling silver circles add a bit of modern adornment to your lobes. These simple post earrings are approximately .5" in diameter. Circles, posts, and earring backs are all sterling silver.

name: Rose Quartz Drop Earrings
description: Faceted rose quartz stones swing from sterling silver earwires. These earrings measure 1.25" in total length.

name: Asterisk Studs
description: These little sterling silver post earrings are a great way to wear handmade every day. The silver circles are just .25" in diameter and are hand-stamped with tiny asterisks. The stamped motif has been oxidized and the rest of the silver has been polished to a satin finish.

name: Element Earrings
description: Casual, handformed sterling silver rings are accented by lovely little hand-stamped discs. All silver has been oxidized and polished to give these earrings a weathered look. The silver rings are .5" in diameter and dangle freely from sterling earwires. These earrings are 1.75" in total length.

name: Montana Agate Ring
description:
This bold rustic ring features a lovely Montana agate gemstone. The oval cabochon is translucent white, speckled by dark inclusions. The generous sterling silver band has a distressed, "ruffled" edge, and measures .5" wide. All silver has been oxidized and polished to enhance the weathered feel. Due to the width of the band, the fit will feel smaller than normal. You may want to order a whole size larger than your usual finger size. 

Each ring is made to order. Please select the size you'd like and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping. Each gemstone will be a bit different. Please see the last photo for available cabochons.

name: Constellation Earrings
description: Two little labradorite gemstones rest at the ends of sterling silver ovals. The bezel set cabochons are primarily gray in color, but flash turquoise, indigo, green, and violet when they catch the light. The labradorite stones are accentuated by a cluster of oxidized dots. The ovals measure .5" x 1.25" and swing from handformed sterling earwires. The earrings are 1.75" in total length.

name: Turquoise Landscape Ring
description:
A gorgeous slab of Chinese turquoise is surrounded in softly oxidized sterling silver. Since each stone is different, each ring is completely unique. This ring's rustic quality is offset by a bit of feminine detail in the scalloped edge of the sterling silver bezel setting. The gemstone and setting measure approximately 1" x 7/8", and the generous band measures 3/8". Due to the width of the band, it is recommended that you order a half size larger than you normally wear.

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping. As seen in the last photo, this ring can be made with a variety of different turquoise stones, and no two are quite alike. If you have a preference as to the coloring in your stone, please e-mail me after ordering, and I will do my best to accommodate your request!

name: Open Air Earrings
description: Casual, handformed sterling silver rings are accented by lovely little nuggets of genuine turquoise. The rings have been oxidized and polished to give them a weathered look. The silver rings are .5" in diameter and dangle freely from sterling earwires. These earrings are 1.5" in total length.

name: Oyster Ring
description:
An elegant freshwater pearl rests gently in a sterling silver "shell." The sterling silver has been carefully shaped to create an imperfect, organic form, which seems to protect the lovely centerpiece. It has also been given a soft patina to add to its natural quality and contrast with the freshwater pearl. The silver "shell" is approximately .5" in diameter and rests on a round sterling silver band. 

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping.

name: Encompass Earrings
description: Sterling silver discs are layered and domed and stamped with a ring of tiny dots. The silver has been oxidized and polished to accentuate the simple details of these earrings. The discs are .75" in diameter and swing from handformed sterling earwires.

name: Confection Necklace
description:
This necklace is simply decadent. The plump ocean jasper gemstone contains a whimsical circular pattern in lovely hues of soft purple and orange. The unique stone is crowned with a sweetly scalloped sterling silver bezel setting which measures 1 1/8" x 7/8". The pendant is suspended on an 18" sterling chain which can be shortened upon request.

Only two available.

name: Stamped Vine Necklace
description: The perfect combination of modern design and vintage appeal...an ornate leaf and vine pattern has been pressed into a simple silver disc. The pendant slides along its chain on a tube bail, which gives it a contemporary edge. The recessed areas of the decorative design have been oxidized while the smooth areas of the pendant have been polished to a satin finish. The disc is .999 fine silver and measures .75" in diameter. The tube bail, chain, and findings are all sterling silver. This necklace is 18" in total length, but can be shortened upon request.

name: Stamped Square Earrings
description: Sterling silver squares have been hand stamped with a lovely decorative at the corners, then slightly domes to add dimension.  Both the stamped motifs and handformed earwires have been oxidized to give the earrings a bit of contrast. The domed squares measure a generous 1"x1," but are light enough for everyday wear.

name: Twig Bracelet
description:
This simple bangle bracelet takes on a charming, rustic quality with a lovely twig-like texture. The bracelet is made from sterling silver which has been carefully hammered with a variety of marks to create a natural look. The silver has then been oxidized and polished to draw attention to the detail of the surface. Casual and unassuming, this bracelet is the perfect way to wear handmade every day.

The bracelet has an outer circumference of 8", and so has slightly smaller interior measurement.

name: Bubble Necklace
description: A variety of sterling silver circles have been soldered together into a modern, yet organic composition. While the pendant is sizable and eye-catching, its negative spaces keep it light enough to wear every day. The pendant measures just over 1.5" at its widest point. The necklace is finished by sterling silver rolo chain and a sterling trigger clasp. Necklace measures approximately 17.5" in total length.

name: Skinny Silver Stacking Rings
description:
These five skinny sterling bands really make a statement when stacked together. They each have a hammered texture which gives them an almost faceted quality when placed next to each other. Whether you choose to wear them together, individually, or stacked with your other rings, you'll find yourself wearing these little silver bands every day of the week. The rings are each approximately 1/16" wide. 

This listing is for a set of five stacking rings, which are made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your rings before shipping.

name: Western Sky Earrings
description: Weathered and rugged and pretty as a moonlit night, these sterling silver earrings have been hand-stamped with a border of tiny little stars. The sterling silver has been oxidized and polished by hand to bring out the unique details of the earrings and to give them a well-worn quality. The earrings are just shy of 1" at their widest point and measure approximately 1.5" in total length.

name: Silver Pinned Bracelet
description: This silver bracelet has a distinctly organic feel. Sterling silver has been hammered and curved to fit your wrist, and the hammered texture is interrupted throughout by several buds of sterling silver. These pins pass through the bracelet and each has a little room to move in its space, adding charming, kinetic quality to the piece. All silver has been given a soft patina to give the bracelet a natural, weathered quality. The two hammered halves of the bracelet are linked together and close with a small sterling trigger clasp. Bracelet is approximately 5mm wide and fits up to 7.5" around.

name: Nucleus Necklace
description: This unique pendant displays a captivating labradorite gemstone, tucked into sterling silver surroundings. The raised wall of the pendant seems to protect the iridescent stone, which is primarily gray in color, but flashes blue, green, and gold when it catches the light.  Tiny dots surround the bezel setting, adding texture and detail. A soft patina gives the necklace an aged, organic quality. The pendant measures approximately 1"x1" and the necklace is 18" in total length, finished by a sterling silver toggle clasp.

name: Polka Dot Saucer Ring
description:
This sterling silver ring is simple and whimsical. A small silver saucer has been stamped with a charming polka dot motif, and sits atop a slim sterling band. The interior of the saucer has been oxidized and polished to bring out the pattern. The small saucer measures approximately 3/8" in diameter.

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping.

name: Big Prehnite Ring
description:
A large, luminous prehnite stone practically glows from its sterling silver bezel setting. At 12mm in diameter, this gorgeous green gemstone really makes an impact, but does not overwhelm. The handmade silver band, at 4mm wide, gives the ring a stronger look and nice weight on your hand, creating a ring that is perfectly suited for special occasions or every day wear. 

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping.

name: Little Pocket Necklace
description: The circular pendant of this charming and whimsical necklace has been formed into a small pocket of sterling silver. The edges of the pocket are accented by a decorative hand stamped border. A bit smaller than the original Pocket Necklace, the pendant measures .75" in diameter and hangs from an 18" sterling silver chain which can be shortened upon request. What this little space might contain is up to you...

name: Calyx Ring
description:
While certainly bold and absolutely eye catching, this stunning ring is still casual at heart. Generous layers of sterling silver have been hand forged into a modern botanic medallion measuring 1.25" in diameter. The simple, modern shapes are offset by a soft patina, which gives the ring a rustic, well-loved quality. A weathered, oversize, square sterling band completes the piece.

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping.

name: Green Sea Glass Ring
description:
This bold and distinctive ring features a piece of pale green sea glass surrounded in sterling silver. The soothing green hue and soft translucent quality of the water-worn glass lend an elegant quality to the piece, while the oversized sterling plate and generous silver band give the ring weight and substance.  The recessed areas of the ring have been given a soft patina to add to the organic quality of the design.

Each ring is made to order. Since each piece of sea glass will have its own unique, irregular shape, your ring may not look exactly like the item pictured, but will surely be one of a kind. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping.

name: Aquamarine and Silver Ring
description:
The simple combination of cool, translucent blue and shining silver creates a ring that is unassuming, yet absolutely captivating. A gorgeous oval aquamarine gemstone rests atop a generous sterling silver band. The handmade silver band, at 4mm wide, gives the ring a stronger look and nice weight on your hand. The smooth cabochon gemstone measures 8 x 10 mm, creating a ring that is substantial, but not overwhelming; perfectly suited for special occasions or every day wear. 

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping.

name: Sunstone Oval Ring
description:
The contrast of luminous sunstone against oxidized silver creates a simple ring that possesses a rustic elegance. The stunning sunstone cabochon seems to sparkle from within, as vibrant orange hues gently transition into golden shimmer. The stone rests atop a generous sterling silver band which has been given a soft patina to further accentuate the brilliance of the sunstone. The smooth cabochon gemstone measures 8 x 10 mm,  creating a ring that is substantial, but not overwhelming; perfectly suited for special occasions or every day wear.

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping.

name: Forsyth Earrings
description: While sleek and modern in design, these elongated earrings maintain their handmade charm with a whimsical stamped design at the bottom of each curved rectangle. The stamped pattern is emphasized by a dark patina, while the reminder of the rectangle has been polished to a satin finish.  The rectangles are 1.25" long and swing from dark handformed earwires. Earrings are 1 7/8" in total length.

name: Nesting Ring
description:
This sterling silver ring takes on a distinctly modern feel with two circular saucers nestled one inside the other. The little domes sit atop a slim sterling band and the ring has been oxidized and polished by hand to accentuate the simple forms. The larger dome measures approximately .5" in diameter.

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping.

name: Opal Stud Earrings
description: These simple stud earrings feature a pair of pretty little imitation opals. The sparkling iridescent stones are only 4mm in diameter, making these earrings perfect for everyday wear. Settings, posts and earrings backs are all sterling silver.

name: Silver Horseshoe Earrings
description:
These small silver earrings are full of natural, rustic charm. The focal points of these unassuming earrings are Hill Tribe Silver rondelle beads. These beads are made by the Karen Hill Tribe in northern Thailand using traditional tribal methods passed down from generation to generation and helps to provide the Karen people with a reliable source of income. The silver content in these Hill Tribes silver beads is typically higher than sterling and they possess a lovely handmade quality. 

The horseshoe shaped earwires are sterling silver and have been handformed and hammered to keep the silver beads from sliding off and to help them stay put in your earlobes. (A pair of clear plastic earring backs will also be included. You may wish to wear them to keep the earrings extra secure.) These earrings are .75" in length and so light and comfortable that you'll want to wear them every day.

name: Ametrine Nugget Bracelet
description: The focal point of this unique bracelet is a pair of beautiful ametrine gemtones which sparkle in hues of lavender and golden yellow. The roughly faceted stones sit alongside a hammered sterling silver ring, all of which are suspended between generous sterling silver chains. The bracelet is finished by a sterling silver S-clasp and a smaller ametrine charm. All silver has been oxidized to contrast with the elegance of the stones and to give this bracelet a more organic quality. The bracelet will fit up to 8" around.

name: Silver Dot Earrings
description: These simple, modern earrings feature small silver dots, which rest and the ends of elongated sterling earwires. These earrings measure just over 1" in total length, making them perfect for everyday wear.

name: Urchin Earrings
description: These playful little earrings feature a modern dot design; hand-stamped, then oxidized to accentuate the pattern. The sterling silver domes are .5" in diameter and have a brushed finish, for a more casual feel. The handformed earwires are also .5" in diameter, making these earrings approximately 1" in total length.

name: Confection Ring
description:
This ring is simply decadent. The plump ocean jasper gemstone contains a whimsical circular pattern in lovely hues of soft purple and orange. The unique stone is surrounded by a sweetly scalloped sterling silver bezel setting, which has been softly oxidized to give the piece an organic quality. The gemstone and setting measure approximately 7/8" x 3/4", and the generous band measures 1/4". 

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping. 

Only three available.

name: Pebble Earrings
description: These little stud earrings are composed of two small pebbles of sterling silver. The larger pebble measures 5mm in diameter while the smaller measures just 2mm. Each earring is 7mm in total length and they have been oxidized and polished to bring out the delicate organic texture.

name: Turquoise Ring Set
description:
This richly colored ring set features a pair of Chinese Turquoise stones. The larger gemstone is 14mm in diameter, while it's companion measures just 5mm across. Both stones are bezel set on sterling silver bands.

As seen in the last photo, some stones are more heavily veined with black, while others transition smoothly between their lighter and darker hues. Please let me know if you have a preference as to the look of your turquoise stone.

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your rings before shipping.

name: Shelter Necklace
description: An imperfect sterling circle encloses two small granules of silver. A tube bail adds structure and detail. The pendant glides along an 18" sterling silver chain (which can be shortened upon request), and the pendant has been oxidized to accentuate the dimension of the small forms. At just 5/8" in diameter, this small pendant is perfect for everyday wear.

name: Riverbed Earrings
description: Two wonderfully irregular ovals of brushed sterling silver have been interrupted throughout by tiny oxidized notches. The ovals are generous in size at approximately 1" wide and 1 1/8" long, but are very light and easy to wear. The ovals swing freely from handformed earwires, making these earrings over 2" in total length.

name: Prairie Bracelet
description: Rugged, yet feminine, this bracelet is perfect for everyday wear. A beautifully textured piece of sterling silver has been riveted to soft, distressed leather. The silver has been pressed with the pattern of a vintage paper doily, then oxidized and polished to bring out the detail of the texture. The bracelet is finished with sterling endcaps and a toggle clasp, and measures 3/8" wide and 7.5" in total length.

name: Curio Earrings
description: These cute, casual earrings will add just a little pop of color to your lobes. The earrings are available in 4 different gemstones: soft aqua amazonite, faceted orange-toned red aventurine, faceted dark pink tourmaline, and deep green African jade. The gemstones are captured by a tiny nugget of sterling silver, on sterling silver hoops that measure approximately .5" in diameter.

name: Silver Dome Ring, Sunrise Motif
description:
With its combination of clean lines and rustic charm, this silver ring will quickly become the piece of jewelry you won't want to be without. The sterling dome has been hand stamped with a pattern of circles, dots, and radiating lines. The dome is surrounded by a .75" silver plate, which gives the piece a feeling of weight and structure. The entire ring has been oxidized and polished by hand to accentuate the detail of the stamped motif and to give the ring a lovely, aged quality. 

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping.

name: Vintage Glass Ring
description:
With its bold color and delicate detail, this fanciful ring will make a unique addition to any jewelry collection. A vintage etched glass cabochon features an ornate three-dimensional floral motif. This beautiful bright pink treasure is set in a sterling silver bezel with a beaded border, for added vintage appeal. The bezel measures just over 1" wide, and all silver has been oxidized and polished to give this piece an aged quality.

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping.

name: Ripple Ring
description:
An organic freshwater pearl is set in a modern sterling silver bezel. The rectangular pearl measures approximately .75" wide and rests atop a slightly distressed, slightly square band. All silver has been given a satin finish.

Each ring is made to order. Please select your size below and allow approximately one week for the creation of your ring before shipping.

name: Rustic Lace Necklace
description: Rustic, yet pretty...bold, yet effortless...this irregular sterling silver pendant has been been pressed with a vintage lace texture. The lovely feminine pattern contrasts beautifully with the rugged genuine leather cord. The silver pendant has been oxidized and polished to accentuate the detail of the texture and to give it a weathered quality. This necklace is 18" in length and is finished by a sterling silver hook-and-eye clasp.
